{"tid":2107812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍兩個月內第5度墜機 一架F-16戰機於新墨西哥州基地墜毀","createTime":"2020-07-14T06:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T12:18:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9937dc7454b1a48f99410f3d6d76b2d5984a0dad","tid":2107812,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:27:27.000Z","msg":"《福斯新聞》報導，美國軍方發布聲明指出，美國空軍新墨西哥州基地發生F-16墜毀事件，事件發生在當地時間週一傍晚，一架F-16戰機墜毀，飛行員彈出並受到輕傷，這是美國空軍5月份以來第5次戰機墜毀，也是過去2週內第二起F-16戰機墜毀。美國軍方表示，目前事發原因正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3227842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3227842&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=8f4d3eb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3227842&h=f3f1a3e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3227842</a><br />\n<br />\n差唔多一個禮拜墜一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c05fe4532133a913868956b142c8441ab1ef78","tid":2107812,"uid":301585,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"又係時候加軍費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國佬咁搞遲早破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a8daeb82e2155077933079ab64ad8f3ae2d024","tid":2107812,"uid":143343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb66717728555f1455d38004b92290248ca05367","tid":2107812,"uid":290883,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"訓練時候墮五架，真正作戰時可以 少 墮50架，"},{"pid":"7710062a48efe4c157051d548556608d7c82f4fe","tid":2107812,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"人冇事咪算好"},{"pid"